title: How do I get an S+ for this!?!!?
body: Title says it all - My score is so good yet I dont get an S+ or even an S. This system is fuarked. I just want one more token to get level 7 for maximum BM :(

replies.body: Try placing more wards and getting better at your csing
Try not being so toxic and look at your cs :D!
It's your CS (should be closer to 200 especially for a midlaner) and probably your deaths too. If GPM was taken into account you probably would've received an S though.
CS is way too low. It should be around 120-160 for 20 mins.
Played another game and got an S, but like my CS was shit cuz I was APC Karthus and I hate CSing with Karthus anyway thanks all
